org.adroitlogic.ultraesb.core.work

Interface WorkManager

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.springframework.beans.factory.Aware, org.springframework.beans.factory.BeanNameAware, ConfigurationElement, java.util.concurrent.Executor, org.springframework.core.task.TaskExecutor, org.adroitlogic.ultraesb.jmx.element.WorkManagerMXBean
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    SimpleQueueWorkManager

    public interface WorkManager
extends ConfigurationElement, org.adroitlogic.ultraesb.jmx.element.WorkManagerMXBean, org.springframework.core.task.TaskExecutor, java.util.concurrent.Executor
    A WorkManager maintains a queue of messages for a ProxyService. It will manage an own thread pool (by way of a Spring TaskExecutor). It may choose to support persistence and crash resilience and priorities for messages.

      • submitNewMessage

        void submitNewMessage(org.adroitlogic.ultraesb.core.MessageImpl msg,
                    boolean useNewThread)
                      throws org.adroitlogic.ultraesb.core.work.WorkException
        Submit a new message for processing. A new message 'may' be persisted for crash resilience by the WorkManager if its configured for crash recovery support. A message priority 'may' be honored by the WorkManager when processing new messages
        Parameters:
        msg - The new message submitted for processing
        useNewThread - true - WorkManager should process the message in a new thread, false - use caller thread
        Throws:
        WorkException - if the message is rejected for any reason - typically when load bounds are exceeded

      • submitAsync

        void submitAsync(org.adroitlogic.ultraesb.core.MessageImpl msg,
               java.lang.Runnable task)
        Submit a task for asynchronous execution by this work manager
        Parameters:
        msg - the message to be made available to the async thread, also as a thread local variable
        task - a Runnable task to be executed asynchronously

      • handleFailedMessage

        void handleFailedMessage(org.adroitlogic.ultraesb.core.MessageImpl msg)

        Parameters:
